cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a fundamental problem of machine learning, which is dimensionality reduction, and proposes a simple multilayer network for this purpose. The paper also mentions the recent breakthrough of artificial intelligence triggered by multilayer neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of the proposed method on image and document data, which suggests the sub-categories cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as likely options. Finally, the paper discusses the training method and the potential broad use of the described method, which suggests the sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible option.
